  "instructions": [
    "Thread datterini tomatoes, mozzarella cheese, and garlic onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together Ponzu sauce, yuzu juice (if using), and sesame seeds (if using).",
    "Brush the skewers with the Ponzu mixture, making sure to coat each piece evenly.",
    "Drizzle sesame oil (if using) and infused oil over the skewers.",
    "Sprinkle chopped green onion and salt over the skewers.",
    "Grill or broil the skewers over medium heat for 2-3 minutes per side, or until the cheese is melted and the tomatoes are slightly charred.",
    "Transfer the skewers to a serving platter and garnish with chopped fresh basil and cherry tomatoes (if using)."
